TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT TTTIM_TIME.DAY_DT as DAY_DT, TTTIM_TIME.MONTH_NR as MONTH_NR, TTTIM_TIME.MONTH_LAST_DT as MONTH_LAST_DT, TTTIM_TIME.YEAR_NR as YEAR_NR, TTTIM_TIME.YEAR_DAYS_QY as YEAR_DAYS_QY, TTTIM_TIME.TIME_PERIOD_ID as TIME_PERIOD_ID FROM TTTIM_TIME WHERE TIME_PERIOD_TYPE_CD='Mon'--

TRANSFORMFIELD.DESCRIPTION: Raghu- 11-22-2005 Changed the logic here as the SQL is changed to incorporate the actual logic
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: INVOICE_ITEM_SEQ_NR

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(ENTRY_MODE_CD='J',TO_CHAR(0),IIF(REVENUE_TYPE_CD = 'PR' AND (ITEM_TYPE_CD ='P' OR ITEM_TYPE_CD ='R'),to_cHAR(PREM_GROSS_LOCAL_AM),IIF(REVENUE_TYPE_CD = 'ZZZ' AND (ENTRY_MODE_CD ='D' OR ENTRY_MODE_CD ='R'),TO_CHAR(PREM_GROSS_LOCAL_AM),TO_CHAR(0))))
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: OUT_PREM_GROSS_LOCAL_AM

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(REVENUE_TYPE_CD= 'PR' AND (BILLING_TYPE_CD ='A' OR BILLING_TYPE_CD ='B' OR BILLING_TYPE_CD ='N' OR BILLING_TYPE_CD ='S' OR BILLING_TYPE_CD ='V' OR BILLING_TYPE_CD ='Y' OR BILLING_TYPE_CD ='9'),PREM_GROSS_LOCAL_AM1,0)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: PrimiumAdministrativeFees

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(ENTRY_MODE_CD='J',TO_CHAR(0),IIF(REVENUE_TYPE_CD = 'PR' AND (ITEM_TYPE_CD ='P' OR ITEM_TYPE_CD ='R'),TO_CHAR(PREM_NET_LOCAL_AM),IIF(REVENUE_TYPE_CD = 'ZZZ' AND (ENTRY_MODE_CD ='D' OR ENTRY_MODE_CD ='R'),TO_CHAR(PREM_NET_LOCAL_AM),TO_CHAR(0))))
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: NetPremium

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: iif(ENTRY_MODE_CD ='J' AND (not isnull (JOURNAL_ENTRY_REASON_CD)), decode( JOURNAL_ENTRY_REASON_CD, '01','01-Defer-Rev Cap JE', '02','02-Defer-Multi Yr JE', '03','03-Rev Allocation JE', '04','04-Bermuda JE', '05','05-Budget Protect JE', '06','06-Income Accrual JE', '07','07-Pass Thru Exp JE', '08','08-Countersign JE', '09','09-Proprietary JE', '10','10-Predate JE', '11','11-ATB Forfeiture JE',NULL),NULL)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: Out_Src_Transaction_CD_Tx

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
SELECT ttptr.srce_profit_center_nr local_office_code,
(SELECT ttcli.source_profit_center_nr FROM cbr2v2_rpt.ttcli_client ttcli WHERE ttcli.client_id = ttptr.client_id AND ttcli.client_hier_level_cd = 'C') source_profit_center_nr,
(SELECT ttcli.client_nr FROM cbr2v2_rpt.ttcli_client ttcli WHERE ttcli.client_id = ttptr.client_id AND ttcli.client_hier_level_cd = 'C') client_nr,
ttptr.srce_department_nr local_department_number,
DECODE (SUBSTR (ttptr.production_cd, 1, 1), 'Z', 'N/A', SUBSTR (ttptr.production_cd, 1, 1) ) local_production_code,
DECODE (SUBSTR (ttptr.duration_cd, 1, 1), 'Z', 'N/A', SUBSTR (ttptr.duration_cd, 1, 1) ) local_duration_code,
(SELECT ttprl.detail_class_cd FROM cbr2v2_rpt.ttprl_product_line ttprl WHERE ttprl.product_id = ttptr.product_id AND ttprl.product_hier_type_cd = 'CLREV') local_detail_prodt_class_code,
ttptr.entry_mode_cd local_entry_mode_code,
NVL (TRIM (ttptr.billing_type_cd), 'N/A') local_transaction_bill_type,
ttptr.invoice_nr transaction_id,
CASE WHEN (ttptr.install_ref_nr = ttptr.invoice_nr ) THEN ttptr.install_hdr_version_nr ELSE ttptr.invoice_hdr_version_nr END transaction_header_ver_number,
DECODE (ttptr.entry_mode_cd, 'B', ttptr.invoice_item_seq_nr, ttptr.tran_item_seq_nr ) transaction_line_number,
ttptr.invoice_item_version_nr transaction_line_ver_number,
ttptr.acctng_period_month_nr accounting_period_month,
ttptr.acctng_period_year_nr accounting_period_year,
ttptr.revenue_type_cd,
(SELECT tteml.srce_employee_nr FROM cbr2v2_rpt.tteml_employee tteml, cbr2v2_rpt.ttcli_client ttcli WHERE ttcli.client_id = ttptr.client_id AND tteml.employee_id = ttcli.acct_producer_employee_id) account_representative_id,
(SELECT REPLACE (tteml.employee_full_nm, '"', '\"' ) FROM cbr2v2_rpt.tteml_employee tteml, cbr2v2_rpt.ttcli_client ttcli WHERE ttcli.client_id = ttptr.client_id AND tteml.employee_id = ttcli.acct_producer_employee_id) account_representative_name,
(SELECT ttitd.reinsurance_in FROM cbr2v2_rpt.ttitd_income_transaction_dtl ttitd WHERE ttitd.invoice_nr = ttptr.invoice_nr AND ttitd.srce_profit_center_nr = ttptr.srce_profit_center_nr AND ttitd.invoice_hdr_version_nr = ttptr.invoice_hdr_version_nr AND ttitd.invoice_item_seq_nr = ttptr.invoice_item_seq_nr AND ttitd.invoice_item_version_nr = ttptr.invoice_item_version_nr AND ttitd.client_id = ttptr.client_id) reinsurance_indicator,
ttptr.ccy_cd transaction_currency_code,
ttptr.recv_local_am gross_revenue, ttptr.shrd_local_am shared_revenue,
ttptr.revenue_local_am net_revenue,
NVL (ttptr.prem_gross_local_am, 0) gross_premium, ttptr.prem_gross_local_am administrative_fees, NVL (ttptr.prem_net_local_am, 0) net_premium,
NVL (TO_CHAR ((SELECT ttcar.corp_carrier_nr FROM cbr2v2_rpt.ttcar_carrier ttcar WHERE ttcar.carrier_id = ttptr.carrier_id AND ttcar.row_display_cd = 'C') ), 'N/A' ) local_carrier_id,
NVL ((SELECT ttcar.corp_carrier_nm FROM cbr2v2_rpt.ttcar_carrier ttcar WHERE ttcar.carrier_id = ttptr.carrier_id AND ttcar.row_display_cd = 'C'), 'N/A' ) local_carrier_name,
NVL ((SELECT ttcar.corp_carrier_nr FROM cbr2v2_rpt.ttcar_carrier ttcar WHERE ttcar.carrier_id = ttptr.payto_id), 'N/A') local_payto_id,
NVL ((SELECT ttcar.corp_carrier_nm FROM cbr2v2_rpt.ttcar_carrier ttcar WHERE ttcar.carrier_id = ttptr.payto_id), 'N/A') local_payto_name,
REPLACE (ttptr.policy_nr, '|', '\|') insurer_policy_number,
ttptr.policy_seq_nr invoicing_system_policy_number,
DECODE (ttptr.cvge_eff_start_dt, TO_DATE ('01/01/0001', 'MM/DD/YYYY'), TO_DATE ('01/01/1900', 'MM/DD/YYYY' ), ttptr.cvge_eff_start_dt ) coverage_start_date,
DECODE (ttptr.cvge_eff_end_dt, TO_DATE ('01/01/0001', 'MM/DD/YYYY'), TO_DATE ('12/31/9999', 'MM/DD/YYYY' ), ttptr.cvge_eff_end_dt ) coverage_end_date,
CASE WHEN ttptr.entry_mode_cd='B' AND ttptr.install_ref_nr = ttptr.invoice_nr AND to_number(ttptr.install_ref_nr) != 0 THEN (SELECT to_date(to_char(ttipd.billing_period_start_dt,'mm/dd/yyyy'),'mm/dd/yyyy') FROM TTIPD_INSTALLMENT_DTL ttipd WHERE ttipd.client_id = ttptr.client_id AND ttipd.install_ref_nr = ttptr.install_ref_nr AND ttipd.install_hdr_version_nr = ttptr.install_hdr_version_nr AND ttipd.billing_item_nr = ttptr.invoice_item_seq_nr AND ttipd.install_correction_version_nr = ttptr.invoice_item_version_nr AND ttipd.install_policy_key_nr = ttptr.install_policy_key_nr) ELSE DECODE(ttptr.entry_mode_cd, 'R',to_date(to_char('01/01/0001'),'mm/dd/yyyy'), 'D',to_date(to_char('01/01/0001'),'mm/dd/yyyy'), 'J',to_date(to_char('01/01/0001'),'mm/dd/yyyy'), to_date(to_char('01/01/0001'),'mm/dd/yyyy') ) END billing_period_start_date,
ttptr.tran_remarks_tx comments, ttptr.item_type_cd,
CASE WHEN ttptr.item_type_cd <> '-' AND ttptr.shrd_usd_am <> 0 THEN 'Y' ELSE 'N' END discount_commission_in,
tran_item_seq_nr, ttptr.install_policy_key_nr, ttptr.TIME_PERIOD_ID AS source_time_period, ttptr.JOURNAL_ENTRY_REASON_CD, ttptr.INSTALL_REF_NR FROM ttptr_mtd_rev_transaction ttptr WHERE ttptr.client_id <> 0 AND ( (time_period_id in (select distinct time_period_id from RM_BASYS_EXTRACT_CONTROL_STBE where REVENUE_MASTER_PICK_UP_IN = 'N')) OR (ttptr.last_update_dt > TO_DATE ('$$BEGIN_DATE', 'mm/dd/yyyy hh24:mi:ss') AND ttptr.last_update_dt <= TO_DATE ('$$END_DATE', 'mm/dd/yyyy hh24:mi:ss')) )
